Replace the single generic \'93brings expertise\'85\'94 sentence with something derived from the author: e.g. domains, tones, and a 1\'962 sentence \'93why I\'92m here\'94 or \'93what I care about\'94 (could be a new field or a shortened bio_80w).\
Optionally support a first-person variant for opinion authors (e.g. \'93When I worked with people in similar situations\'85\'94).\
